Comparing and Profiling Entity Component Systems (ECS): EntityX, Anax, Artemis

	Provides example code to compare the APIs of these ECS as well as allowing to benchmark them in a comparable manner.


URL for the article discussing this project:
	http://tilemapkit.com/2015/10/entity-component-systems-compared-benchmarked-entityx-anax-artemis

Previous article that explains how to install these ECS in a project:
	http://tilemapkit.com/2015/10/install-entity-component-systems-anax-entityx-artemis/

The articles include the links to the respective ECS' github repositories. Tested with Xcode 7 and XC unit tests for benchmarking.
